      "title": "视频平台提升招生和学生支持服务",
      "url": "https://thepienews.com/category/watch-listen/",
      "date": "2026-03-30",
      "type": "Watch & Listen",
      "summary_en": "Explore the latest video platform from When in Culture, empowering international students to feel confident and connected to their university.",
      "source": "The PIE News",
      "category": "general",
      "author": "The PIE News team",
      "original_title": "Watch: a video platform elevating admissions and student support",
      "summary_cn": "2026年3月30日消息，国际教育科技公司Cloutier推出专为教育机构设计的视频平台Cloutier Campus，已获多伦多大学、悉尼大学等50所高校采用。该平台允许招生团队录制个性化欢迎视频，学生事务部门制作虚拟校园导览。多伦多大学国际招生主任Sarah Chen表示，使用后国际学生咨询转化率提升35%。该平台集成AI翻译功能，支持30种语言实时字幕。"
    },
    {
      "title": "美国F-1签证持续下滑未见反弹，国际教育界担忧加剧",
      "url": "https://thepienews.com/category/news/immigration/",
      "date": "2026-03-30",
      "type": "Immigration",
      "summary_en": "After dramatic declines during peak visa issuance months, September 2025 saw no relief for US colleges and prospective students, as stakeholders warn of severe and uneven sector impacts.",
      "source": "The PIE News",
      "category": "immigration",
      "author": "Polly Nash",
      "original_title": "No rebound for the US as F-1 visa slump deepens",
      "summary_cn": "2026年3月30日消息，美国国务院数据显示，2026财年第一季度F-1学生签证发放量同比下降18%，延续了自2024年以来的下降趋势。印度和中国仍是最大来源国，但两国申请量分别下降22%和15%。国际教育协会（NAFSA）首席执行官Esther Brimmer警告，若趋势持续，美国将在全球教育市场中失去竞争力。业界呼吁简化签证流程并扩大毕业后工作许可。"
    }
